member.example:
Sending data in application/json:
{ title:"My post", content:"Post content", tags:"Me,Post,News", subscribeComments: "true" }
Sending data in application/x-www-form-urlencoded title="My post"&content="Post content"&tags="Me,Post,News"&subscribeComments="true"

Sending data in application/json:
{ content:"My comment", parentId:"9924256A-739C-462b-AF15-E652A3B1B6EB" }
Sending data in application/x-www-form-urlencoded content="My comment"&parentId="9924256A-739C-462b-AF15-E652A3B1B6EB"

Sending data in application/json:
{ content:"My comment", parentId:"9924256A-739C-462b-AF15-E652A3B1B6EB" }
Sending data in application/x-www-form-urlencoded content="My comment"&parentId="9924256A-739C-462b-AF15-E652A3B1B6EB"

Sending data in application/json:
{ url:"www.teamlab.com", title: "TeamLab", description: "best site i've ever seen", tags: "project management, collaboration" }
Sending data in application/x-www-form-urlencoded url="www.teamlab.com"&title="TeamLab"&description="best site i've ever seen"&tags="project management, collaboration"

Sending data in application/json:
{ content:"My comment", parentId:"9924256A-739C-462b-AF15-E652A3B1B6EB" }
